Citations of reference are not strictly required on the Bitcoin wiki (in contrast to, say, Wikipedia). But using a <nowiki>{{cite}}</nowiki> tag on a piece of unsourced information may be useful if it is in a gray area somewhere between misinformation and word-of-mouth, yet could be truthful and worth keeping.

